verbose_text: In the present study, BCA significantly reduced the serum production of IL-1beta, IL-18, IL-6 and TNF-alpha, inhibited the expression levels of TLR4, MyD88, NLRP3, ASC, caspase-1 and the phosphorylations of IkB-alpha and NF-kB in MI/R rats.
